headline: Democratic senators press Commerce Secretary Lutnick on conflict of interest concerns in USA Rare Earth deal
summary: Sens. Elizabeth Warren, Chris Van Hollen and Ron Wyden are pressing Commerce Secretary Howard Lutnick for more information on the USA Rare Earth deal.
